00:19:19.800 --> 00:19:23.080 align:middle line:90%


00:19:23.080 --> 00:19:29.040 align:middle line:84%
So now, we can use
this equation in here,

00:19:29.040 --> 00:19:35.330 align:middle line:84%
because S times psi just
