00:19:49.340 --> 00:19:52.770 align:middle line:90%
We just use that equation.

00:19:52.770 --> 00:19:53.665 align:middle line:90%
Yes?

00:19:53.665 --> 00:19:55.082 align:middle line:84%
STUDENT: I'm a
