00:24:38.585 --> 00:24:41.280 align:middle line:90%


00:24:41.280 --> 00:24:44.930 align:middle line:90%
So now, we can try to--

00:24:44.930 --> 00:24:48.380 align:middle line:90%
so since the S--

00:24:48.380 --> 00:24:52.990 align:middle line:84%
