00:27:54.690 --> 00:28:03.450 align:middle line:84%
So given by i
commutator lambda rho,

00:28:03.450 --> 00:28:18.215 align:middle line:84%
gamma mu equal to eta lambda
mu gamma rho minus rho mu gamma

00:28:18.215 --> 00:28:18.715 align:middle line:90%
lambda.

00:28:18.715 --> 00:28:22.250 align:middle line:90%


00:28:22.250 --> 00:28:23.580 align:middle line:90%
So you get this equation.

00:28:23.580 --> 00:28:27.320 align:middle line:84%
So the left-hand side is
