00:28:51.600 --> 00:28:54.000 align:middle line:90%
So you have some eta here.

00:28:54.000 --> 00:28:56.340 align:middle line:84%
You have eta here,
and yeah, so that's

00:28:56.340 --> 00:28:57.810 align:middle line:90%
