00:28:59.340 --> 00:29:03.115 align:middle line:84%
because it should be
antisymmetric in the--

00:29:03.115 --> 00:29:03.615 align:middle line:90%
yeah.

00:29:03.615 --> 00:29:06.810 align:middle line:90%


00:29:06.810 --> 00:29:07.890 align:middle line:90%
Good.

00:29:07.890 --> 00:29:11.470 align:middle line:84%
So now, it just boils down
to solve this equation.

00:29:11.470 --> 00:29:14.790 align:middle line:90%
So if we can find sigma--

00:29:14.790 --> 00:29:19.670 align:middle line:84%
satisfy this equation,
and then we are done.

00:29:19.670 --> 00:29:23.080 align:middle line:90%


00:29:23.080 --> 00:29:27.460 align:middle line:90%
So yeah, of course, this is--

00:29:27.460 --> 00:29:30.360 align:middle line:84%
now, you do it by
