So these are the generators.

00:35:30.560 --> 00:35:37.280 align:middle line:90%


00:35:37.280 --> 00:35:43.520 align:middle line:90%
So when omega mu nu--

00:35:43.520 --> 00:35:47.390 align:middle line:84%
when the mu nu equal to spatial
