00:35:49.520 --> 00:35:54.860 align:middle line:84%
spatial rotation and the 0
i corresponding to a boost.

00:35:54.860 --> 00:35:56.630 align:middle line:90%
So remember.

00:35:56.630 --> 00:36:04.110 align:middle line:84%
So that means for
