generators of rotations.

00:36:24.910 --> 00:36:29.150 align:middle line:90%


00:36:29.150 --> 00:36:33.250 align:middle line:84%
So remember, previously--
so if you remember

00:36:33.250 --> 00:36:35.560 align:middle line:84%
how we do the Lorentz
transformation,

00:36:35.560 --> 00:36:42.490 align:middle line:84%
