00:39:14.060 --> 00:39:25.370 align:middle line:90%


00:39:25.370 --> 00:39:27.830 align:middle line:90%
So this is not unitary.

00:39:27.830 --> 00:39:31.130 align:middle line:84%
So in general-- so normally,
