00:40:31.685 --> 00:40:38.480 align:middle line:90%


00:40:38.480 --> 00:40:41.030 align:middle line:84%
say S and S dagger
is not equal to 1.

00:40:41.030 --> 00:40:45.400 align:middle line:90%


00:40:45.400 --> 00:40:49.600 align:middle line:90%
