prime slash psi

00:52:32.460 --> 00:52:38.582 align:middle line:84%
prime x prime equal to
S partial slash psi x.

00:52:38.582 --> 00:52:47.970 align:middle line:90%


00:52:47.970 --> 00:52:48.470 align:middle line:90%
Good?

00:52:48.470 --> 00:52:55.320 align:middle line:90%


00:52:55.320 --> 00:52:57.420 align:middle line:84%
So let me just
mention one more thing

00:52:57.420 --> 00:53:00.030 align:middle line:90%
you can work out yourself.

00:53:00.030 --> 00:53:03.030 align:middle line:90%
So you can check--

00:53:03.030 --> 00:53:07.500 align:middle line:84%
so these are all things you
can check yourself once you

00:53:07.500 --> 00:53:09.810 align:middle line:90%
