00:53:21.705 --> 00:53:36.400 align:middle line:90%


00:53:36.400 --> 00:53:44.590 align:middle line:84%
That means psi bar prime
x prime gamma mu psi prime

00:53:44.590 --> 00:54:00.700 align:middle line:84%
x prime is equal to lambda mu
nu psi bar x gamma nu psi x.

00:54:00.700 --> 00:54:03.970 align:middle line:84%
So if you view this
whole thing as a vector,

00:54:03.970 --> 00:54:07.740 align:middle line:84%
and then you see the
prime-- the quantity

00:54:07.740 --> 00:54:11.770 align:middle line:84%
