of S and the relations

00:54:21.300 --> 00:54:25.980 align:middle line:84%
between different gamma
matrices you can just show that.

00:54:25.980 --> 00:54:30.030 align:middle line:90%


00:54:30.030 --> 00:54:30.530 align:middle line:90%
Good.

