00:54:45.985 --> 00:54:50.650 align:middle line:90%


00:54:50.650 --> 00:54:52.500 align:middle line:84%
So now, we can write
down the Dirac action.

00:54:52.500 --> 00:54:57.900 align:middle line:90%


00:54:57.900 --> 00:55:00.040 align:middle line:84%
The action which gives
