get the Dirac equation.

00:59:20.510 --> 00:59:23.730 align:middle line:84%
Then you can also easily
check by integration by part.

00:59:23.730 --> 00:59:28.070 align:middle line:84%
And if you were psi, you get
the complex conjugate version

00:59:28.070 --> 00:59:32.780 align:middle line:84%
of the Dirac equation
acting on psi bar.

00:59:32.780 --> 00:59:35.870 align:middle line:84%
So now let me just
say a few words

00:59:35.870 --> 00:59:37.760 align:middle line:90%
