01:03:33.860 --> 01:03:35.300 align:middle line:90%
So we will see fermions.

01:03:35.300 --> 01:03:38.240 align:middle line:90%
We will see Pauli principle.

01:03:38.240 --> 01:03:42.890 align:middle line:84%
But before-- but
as we said before,

01:03:42.890 --> 01:03:47.550 align:middle line:84%
that when we quantize the
theory, we first need to--

01:03:47.550 --> 01:03:50.100 align:middle line:84%
the simplest way
