01:11:30.250 --> 01:11:39.820 align:middle line:84%
So to find the explicit
form of u and v--

01:11:39.820 --> 01:11:43.710 align:middle line:90%


01:11:43.710 --> 01:11:45.630 align:middle line:84%
so one simple thing
to do is let's

01:11:45.630 --> 01:11:47.850 align:middle line:84%
just consider in
the simple case--

01:11:47.850 --> 01:11:49.830 align:middle line:84%
say, consider the
particle is at rest.

01:11:49.830 --> 01:11:53.550 align:middle line:90%


01:11:53.550 --> 01:11:56.250 align:middle line:84%
When the particle is
at rest, then the omega

01:11:56.250 --> 01:12:01.740 align:middle line:84%
