we have a minus sign here.

01:12:56.030 --> 01:13:00.560 align:middle line:90%


01:13:00.560 --> 01:13:02.240 align:middle line:84%
So essentially,
this just becomes--

01:13:02.240 --> 01:13:04.490 align:middle line:84%
so m can be canceled
on both sides.

01:13:04.490 --> 01:13:08.180 align:middle line:84%
So essentially, it just
becomes the i gamma

01:13:08.180 --> 01:13:16.775 align:middle line:84%
0 u equal to minus u and
i gamma 0 v equal to--

01:13:16.775 --> 01:13:17.275 align:middle line:90%
OK.

01:13:17.275 --> 01:13:27.990 align:middle line:90%


