01:13:41.500 --> 01:13:45.400 align:middle line:84%
And so let's just now--
to write them explicitly.

01:13:45.400 --> 01:13:47.800 align:middle line:84%
So now, let's use the
explicit representation

01:13:47.800 --> 01:13:49.780 align:middle line:90%
of gamma matrices.

01:13:49.780 --> 01:13:51.940 align:middle line:90%
Let me just copy this.

01:13:51.940 --> 01:13:58.210 align:middle line:84%
